INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (1,'2024-07-28 16:54:37','flex','flex 教程','slug-flex 教程','[TOC]\r\n\r\n# flex简介\r\n```\r\n帮助文档\r\nhttps://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1A44y1Z7Bp/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&vd_source=6f7ee9d97e0a5f4d63a72466f30986c5\r\n```\r\n- 优势：\r\n	- flex布局非常高效(float就是过时产物，只有培训机构天天讲)\r\n	- Flexbox 可以轻松地创建响应式布局，而无需使用复杂的浮动或定位技术\r\n	- 它允许你轻松地更改元素的顺序、对齐方式和空间分配\r\n	- Flexbox 允许容器自动调整子元素的大小，以适应可用空间。\r\n	- 它可以很好地处理未知大小的元素和动态内容\r\n	- Flexbox 使得创建响应式布局变得非常容易，可以轻松地适应不同的屏幕尺寸和设备。\r\n	- Flexbox 支持沿主轴和交叉轴的对齐，可以轻松地控制元素的对齐方式\r\n- 吐槽float：\r\n	- 不用考虑兼容ie后，float就跟着ie一起入土了\r\n	- float当初的设计就是为了实现文字环绕图片的效果，历史遗留产物\r\n\r\n# 元素转化为flex容器\r\n```css\r\ndisplay: flex;\r\n或者\r\ndisplay: inline-flex;\r\n```\r\ndiv加上display: flex;就是一个flex容器  \r\nflex容器有主轴和交叉轴  \r\n主轴：就是横向轴  \r\n交叉轴：垂直于主轴的一个轴  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!17_37_57.png \'\'图片title\'\')\r\n\r\n主轴:左边开始 右边结束  \r\n交叉轴：上面开始 下面结束  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!17_41_39.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n\r\n# 创建一个flex  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!17_46_49.png \'\'图片title\'\')\r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"d-container\">\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# flex里面添加三个子flex 横着排列\r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!17_51_20.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n这种本质上就是父元素 排布方式 flex-direction: row;\r\n```\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-direction: row;\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n        .d1,.d2,.d3{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 50px;\r\n            height: 30px;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n        .d1{\r\n            background-color: rgb(185, 243, 224);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d2{\r\n            background-color: rgb(150, 248, 215);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d3{\r\n            background-color: rgb(86, 245, 192);\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"d-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"d1\">1</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d2\">2</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d3\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 反过来排序\r\n主要就是父元素启用 flex-direction:row-reverse;  \r\n主轴的开始结束相互对调  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!17_54_56.png \'\'图片title\'\')\r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-direction:row-reverse;\r\n        }\r\n        .d1,.d2,.d3{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 50px;\r\n            height: 30px;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n        .d1{\r\n            background-color: rgb(185, 243, 224);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d2{\r\n            background-color: rgb(150, 248, 215);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d3{\r\n            background-color: rgb(86, 245, 192);\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"d-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"d1\">1</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d2\">2</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d3\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 三个flex 竖着排列\r\n启用flex-direction:column;  \r\n这个时候主轴 就是竖向的 上面开始 下面结束  \r\n```\r\nflex-direction:column;\r\n```\r\n结果  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!18_02_14.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n完整代码\r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-direction:column;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d1,.d2,.d3{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 50px;\r\n            height: 30px;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d1{\r\n            background-color: rgb(185, 243, 224);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d2{\r\n            background-color: rgb(150, 248, 215);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d3{\r\n            background-color: rgb(86, 245, 192);\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"d-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"d1\">1</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d2\">2</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d3\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 三个flex 竖着排列 反序\r\n启用flex-direction:column-reverse;  \r\n这个时候主轴 就是竖向的 下面开始 上面结束  \r\n结果  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!18_03_16.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n代码\r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        .d-container{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 500px;\r\n            height: 300px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-direction:column-reverse;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d1,.d2,.d3{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 50px;\r\n            height: 30px;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d1{\r\n            background-color: rgb(185, 243, 224);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d2{\r\n            background-color: rgb(150, 248, 215);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d3{\r\n            background-color: rgb(86, 245, 192);\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"d-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"d1\">1</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d2\">2</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d3\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# flex-basis 指定元素宽度\r\nflex-basis: 30px;可以指定每个子flex容器的宽度  \r\n```\r\n父元素\r\ndisplay: flex;\r\nflex-direction:row;\r\n\r\n所有子元素\r\ndisplay: flex;\r\nflex-basis: 30px;\r\n```\r\n结果  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!18_17_57.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n\r\n代码  \r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n\r\n    <style>\r\n        