\"d3 item\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 缩小 flex-shrink\r\n其实如果不处理子元素，子元素宽度超过父元素 就会很不好，我们可以通过设置：flex-shrink: 1;来实现子元素永远在父元素里面  \r\n注意 一旦flex-shrink: 0; 那么对于所有子元素就约束不住了  \r\n```\r\n父元素\r\ndisplay: flex;\r\nflex-direction:row;\r\n\r\n所有子元素\r\ndisplay: flex;\r\nflex-shrink: 1;  保证子元素宽 不超过父元素\r\nflex-basis: 50px;\r\n```\r\n结果  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!20_31_37.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n代码  \r\n```\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Document</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"D:\\2-code\\1-python-pro\\2-virtual\\py3.10.5_The_Avenue\\pro\\src\\website_rsgz_01\\static\\css\\reset.css\">\r\n    <style>\r\n        .fu{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            width: 150px;\r\n            height: 100px;\r\n            background-color: rgb(202, 245, 231);\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-direction:row;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .item{\r\n            display: flex;\r\n            border-radius: 8px;\r\n            flex-shrink: 1;\r\n            flex-basis: 50px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d1{\r\n            background-color: rgb(185, 243, 224);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d2{\r\n            background-color: rgb(150, 248, 215);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .d3{\r\n            background-color: rgb(86, 245, 192);\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .item:nth-child(1){\r\n            /* flex-grow: 100; */\r\n            /*\r\n            150-30*3=60  60/10=6  那么一份就是6\r\n            30+60-12:30+6:30+6\r\n            78:36:36\r\n            */\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"fu\">\r\n        <div class=\"d1 item\">1</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d2 item\">2</div>\r\n        <div class=\"d3 item\">3</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n# 