g\" class=\"header-upload-entry__icon\"><path d=\"M12.0824 10H14.1412C15.0508 10 15.7882 10.7374 15.7882 11.6471V12.8824C15.7882 13.792 15.0508 14.5294 14.1412 14.5294H3.84707C2.93743 14.5294 2.20001 13.792 2.20001 12.8824V11.6471C2.20001 10.7374 2.93743 10 3.84707 10H5.90589\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M8.99413 11.2353L8.99413 3.82353\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M12.0823 6.29413L8.9941 3.20589L5.90587 6.29413\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.7\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>\r\n                <span class=\"header-upload-entry__text\">投稿</span>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        \r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n```',2,'yuuha999','不浪仙人'),(3,'2024-07-28 20:26:58','Flask','Flask 文章视图','slug-Flask 文章视图','[TOC]\r\n\r\n# 请求分类\r\n\r\n## 新建文章\r\nget请求\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"{{ url_for(\'article.article_edit\') }}\">新建文章</a>|\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 编辑单个文章(传id)\r\nget请求\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"{{ url_for(\'article.article_edit_detail\', article_id=article_id) }}\"><span>点击编辑</span></a>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 保存单个文章(传id)\r\npost请求\r\n```\r\n{{ url_for(\'article.article_edit_detail_submit\', article_id=article.id) }}\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 查看单个文章(传id)\r\nget请求\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"{{ url_for(\'article.article_show_detail\', article_id=article.id) }}\">查看文章</a>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 查看一群文章\r\nget请求\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"{{ url_for(\'article.article_set_show\') }}\">查看所有文章</a>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 视图函数分析\r\n\r\n## 公共部分\r\n```\r\nfrom flask import Blueprint,render_template\r\n\r\n# 访问login需要加上前缀 /auth/login\r\nbp = Blueprint(\"article\", __name__, url_prefix=\'/\')\r\n\r\n# 定义错误处理函数\r\n@bp.errorhandler(404)\r\ndef page_not_found(e):\r\n    # 返回自定义的 404 错误页面\r\n    return render_template(\'error/404.html\'), 404\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 新建文章\r\n如果是get 点击 新建文章 获取建立文章的界面  \r\n如果是post 请求 就是文章写好了 发送数据到后端，获取编辑单个文章界面    \r\n```\r\n# http://192.168.0.102:5000/article/edit\r\n@bp.route(\"/article/edit/\",methods=[\'GET\',\'POST\'])\r\n@login_required\r\ndef article_edit():\r\n    if request.method == \'GET\':\r\n        print(\"新建文章\")\r\n        return render_template(\"article/article_xinjian.html\")\r\n    if request.method == \'POST\':\r\n        form = PageArticleForm2(request.form)\r\n        if form.validate():\r\n            title = form.title.data\r\n            print(title)\r\n            content = form.content.data\r\n            tag = form.tag.data\r\n            slug = form.slug.data\r\n            wechat = form.wechat.data\r\n            wechat_public_account = form.wechat_public_account.data\r\n            article = PageArticleModel(title=title, content=content, tag=tag,\r\n                                       slug=slug, wechat=wechat,\r\n                                       wechat_public_account=wechat_public_account,\r\n                                       user_id=g.user.id)\r\n            db.session.add(article)\r\n            db.session.commit()\r\n            print(\"新建文章数据提交成功!!!\")\r\n        else:\r\n            print(form.errors)\r\n\r\n        return redirect(url_for(\"article.article_edit_detail\", article_id=article.id))\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 编辑单个文章(传id)\r\n编辑单个文章 直接就是 get请求，获取编辑文章界面\r\n```\r\n# http://192.168.0.102:5000/article/edit/<article_id>\r\n@bp.route(\"/article/edit/<article_id>/\",methods=[\'GET\'])\r\n@login_required\r\ndef article_edit_detail(article_id):\r\n    if request.method == \'GET\':\r\n        print(\"article_id\",article_id)\r\n        article = PageArticleModel.query.get(article_id)\r\n        print(\"article\",article)\r\n        print(\"article.user_id\", article.user_id)\r\n        article_user = UserModel.query.get(article.user_id)\r\n        return render_template(\"article/article_page_detail_edit.html\", article=article, article_user=article_user)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 保存单个文章(传id)\r\n这个就是post请求，直接返回当前页面 就是编辑文章界面\r\n```\r\n@bp.route(\"/article/edit/submit/\",methods=[\'POST\'])\r\n@login_required\r\n# {{ url_for(\'article.article_edit_detail_submit\') }}\r\ndef article_edit_detail_submit():\r\n    form = PageArticleForm(request.form)\r\n    if form.validate():\r\n        article_id = form.article_id.data\r\n        article = PageArticleModel.query.get(article_id)\r\n        content = form.content.data\r\n        title = form.title.data\r\n        tag = form.tag.data\r\n        slug = form.slug.data\r\n        wechat = form.wechat.data\r\n        wechat_public_account = form.wechat_public_account.data\r\n\r\n        article.content = content\r\n        article.title = title\r\n        article.tag = tag\r\n        article.slug = slug\r\n        article.wechat = wechat\r\n        article.wechat_public_account = wechat_public_account\r\n\r\n        article_user = UserModel.query.get(article.user_id)\r\n        db.session.add(article)\r\n        db.session.commit()\r\n        article_id = article.id\r\n        return redirect(url_for(\"article.article_edit_detail\", article_id=article_id))\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 查看单个文章(传id)\r\n```\r\n@bp.route(\"/article/public/<article_id>\",methods=[\'GET\'])\r\n@login_required\r\ndef article_show_detail(article_id):\r\n    if request.method == \'GET\':\r\n        print(\"进入文章详情页面\")\r\n        article = PageArticleModel.query.get_or_404(article_id)\r\n        article_user = UserModel.query.get(article.user_id)\r\n        return render_template(\'article/article_page_detail.html\',article=article,article_user=article_user,article_id=article_id)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 查看一群文章\r\n```\r\n@bp.route(\"/article/public/\", methods=[\'GET\'])\r\n@login_required\r\ndef article_set_show():\r\n    page = request.args.get(\'page\', 1, type=int)  # 获取当前页码，默认为第一页\r\n    pagination = PageArticleModel.query.order_by(PageArticleModel.creat_time.desc()).paginate(\r\n        page=page, per_page=50, error_out=False)  # 每页显示10篇文章\r\n\r\n    articles = pagination.items  # 当前页的文章列表\r\n    users = [UserModel.query.get(article.user_id) for article in articles]\r\n    return render_template(\'article/articles_show.html\', articles=articles, pagination=pagination, users=users)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n',2,'yuuha999','不浪仙人'),(4,'2024-07-28 22:34:13','头晕,健康','为什么这几天晚上会出现头晕？','slug-为什么这几天晚上会出现头晕？','为什么这几天晚上会出现头晕呢？高血压 低血压 还是心率 还是血管堵塞？还是吹风扇导致的呢，很烦，这种不是发烧的头晕，类似于一种原地转圈那种晕眩。抖音看到有人说是耳石症，前庭神经炎症，颈椎病啥的',2,'yuuha999','不浪仙人'),(5,'2024-07-31 14:35:09','Flask','Flask 上传图片(多种方法实现)','slug-Flask 上传图片(多种方法实现)','[TOC]\r\n\r\n# 核心方法\r\n```\r\n<input type=\"file\" name=\"editormd-image-file\" accept=\"image/*\">\r\n通过name属性值锁定目标\r\nfile = request.files.get(\'editormd-image-file\')\r\nfile = request.files[\'editormd-image-file\']\r\n\r\n如果是存储到本地直接保存\r\nfile.save(\".\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename))\r\n\r\n如果是存储到阿里oss\r\nname 是你自己自定义的新名字\r\nbucket.put_object(name,file)\r\n\r\n最后return的时候 返回一个json\r\nres = {\r\n	\'success\': 1,\r\n	\'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n	\'url\': \"\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename),\r\n	或者\r\n	\'url\': link\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 同域上传图片\r\n这种方式上传 是通过点击![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-07-31!16_23_16.png \'\'图片title\'\') 这个logo 然后慢慢点击选择文件方式上传  不是很喜欢 ，我喜欢直接粘贴的形式  \r\n其中核心方法是：\r\n将上传的图片通过这个方法获取\r\nfile = request.files.get(\'editormd-image-file\')  \r\n保存到本地 改变名字为filename\r\nfile.save(\".\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename))  \r\n\r\nimage 路由  主要作用就是隐藏真是图片路径  \r\n\'success\': 1 一定要填写1/0  \r\n\'url\'一定要返回图片文件的路径  \r\n```\r\n        res = {\r\n            \'success\': 1,\r\n            \'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n            # \'url\': url_for(\'article.image\', name=filename)\r\n            \'url\': \"\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename)\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n# 同域给前端Markdown编辑器返回图片二进制对象\r\n@bp.route(\'/image2/<name>\')\r\ndef image(name):\r\n    with open(os.path.join(\'.\\\\static\\\\upload\', name), \'rb\') as f:\r\n        resp = Response(f.read(), mimetype=\"image/jpeg\")\r\n    return resp\r\n\r\n\r\n# 同域上传图片\r\n@bp.route(\'/upload/\', methods=[\'POST\'])\r\ndef upload_bendi_shangchuan():\r\n    file = request.files.get(\'editormd-image-file\')\r\n    if not file:\r\n        res = {\r\n            \'success\': 0,\r\n            \'message\': \'上传失败\'\r\n        }\r\n    else:\r\n        ex = os.path.splitext(file.filename)[1]\r\n        filename = datetime.now().strftime(\'%Y%m%d%H%M%S\') + ex\r\n        file.save(\".\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename))\r\n        res = {\r\n            \'success\': 1,\r\n            \'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n            # \'url\': url_for(\'article.image\', name=filename)\r\n            \'url\': \"\\\\static\\\\upload\\\\{}\".format(filename)\r\n        }\r\n    return jsonify(res)\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 跨域上传图片-->oss\r\n这个会将选择的图片上传到oss里面  \r\n返回参数的时候 一定要按照这个格式来\r\n```\r\n            res = {\r\n                \'success\': 1,\r\n                \'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n                # 跨域上传只需要返回图像imgUrl即可\r\n                \'url\': link\r\n            }\r\n```\r\n也是通过 file = request.files.get(\'editormd-image-file\')获取file  \r\nfile.filename  # Frame 1.svg 这个可以获取短名称，ali_ret = bucket.put_object(name, file)通过put_object直接上传file  \r\n```\r\n@bp.route(\'/uploads_kuayu/\', methods=[\'POST\'])\r\ndef uploads_kuayu_bieren_xiede():\r\n    file = request.files.get(\'editormd-image-file\')\r\n    if not file:\r\n        res = {\r\n            \'success\': 0,\r\n            \'message\': \'上传失败\'\r\n        }\r\n    else:\r\n        bucket = RunOSS(AccessKeyId=AccessKeyId,\r\n                        AccessKeySecret=AccessKeySecret,\r\n                        Endpoint=Endpoint,\r\n                        BuckerName=BuckerName,\r\n                        filename=\'\').getBucket()\r\n        houzhui = file.filename.split(\'.\')[-1]  # Frame 1.svg\r\n        name = \"falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/{}.{}\".format(get_current_time(), houzhui)\r\n        ali_ret = bucket.put_object(name, file)\r\n        link = r\"http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/\" + name\r\n        # imgUrl = uploadImg(imgData)\r\n        if link:\r\n            res = {\r\n                \'success\': 1,\r\n                \'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n                # 跨域上传只需要返回图像imgUrl即可\r\n                \'url\': link\r\n            }\r\n        else:\r\n            res = {\r\n                \'success\': 0,\r\n                \'message\': \'上传失败\'\r\n            }\r\n    return jsonify(res)\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 粘贴上传到oss\r\njson返回code 200是因为editormd本身没有支持粘贴上传，后面补了一个\r\n```\r\n<script src=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'js/zhantie_shangchuan.js\') }}\"></script>\r\n```\r\nzhantie_shangchuan.js\r\n```\r\nfunction initPasteDragImg(Editor){\r\n    var doc = document.getElementById(Editor.id)\r\n    doc.addEventListener(\'paste\', function (event) {\r\n        var items = (event.clipboardData || window.clipboardData).items;\r\n        var file = null;\r\n        if (items && items.length) {\r\n            // 搜索剪切板items\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\r\n                if (items[i].type.indexOf(\'image\') !== -1) {\r\n                    file = items[i].getAsFile();\r\n                    break;\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        } else {\r\n            console.log(\"当前浏览器不支持\");\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!file) {\r\n            console.log(\"粘贴内容非图片\");\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        uploadImg(file,Editor);\r\n    });\r\n    var dashboard = document.getElementById(Editor.id)\r\n    dashboard.addEventListener(\"dragover\", function (e) {\r\n        e.preventDefault()\r\n        e.stopPropagation()\r\n    })\r\n    dashboard.addEventListener(\"dragenter\", function (e) {\r\n        e.preventDefault()\r\n        e.stopPropagation()\r\n    })\r\n    dashboard.addEventListener(\"drop\", function (e) {\r\n        e.preventDefault()\r\n        e.stopPropagation()\r\n        var files = this.files || e.dataTransfer.files;\r\n        uploadImg(files[0],Editor);\r\n    })\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction uploadImg(file,Editor){\r\n    var formData = new FormData();\r\n    var fileName=new Date().getTime()+\".\"+file.name.split(\".\").pop();\r\n    formData.append(\'image\', file, fileName);\r\n    $.ajax({\r\n        //配置图片上传的接口路径\r\n        url: Editor.settings.imageUploadURL,\r\n        type: \'post\',\r\n        data: formData,\r\n        processData: false,\r\n        contentType: false,\r\n        dataType: \'json\',\r\n        success: function (msg) {\r\n            var code=msg[\'code\'];\r\n            if(code==200){\r\n                var url=msg[\"data\"];\r\n                if(/\\.(png|jpg|jpeg|gif|bmp|ico)$/.test(url)){\r\n                    Editor.insertValue(\"![图片alt](\"+url+\" \'\'图片title\'\')\");\r\n                }else{\r\n                    Editor.insertValue(\"[下载附件](\"+url+\")\");\r\n                }\r\n            }else{\r\n                console.log(msg);\r\n                alert(\"上传失败\");\r\n            }\r\n        },\r\n        error: function () {\r\n            console.log(\'请求失败\');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n具体的flask视图\r\n```\r\n这个对接的是 \'code\': 200\r\nres = {\r\n	\'code\': 200,\r\n	\'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n	\'data\': link\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n@bp.route(\"/uploads_pic_paste_self/\",methods=[\'POST\'])\r\n@login_required\r\ndef uploads_pic_paste_self():\r\n    if request.method == \'POST\':\r\n        img = request.files.get(\'image\')  # <FileStorage: \'1722399349461.png\' (\'image/png\')>\r\n        print(\"img--->\",img)\r\n        bucket = RunOSS(AccessKeyId=AccessKeyId,\r\n                        AccessKeySecret=AccessKeySecret,\r\n                        Endpoint=Endpoint,\r\n                        BuckerName=BuckerName,\r\n                        filename=\'\').getBucket()\r\n        houzhui=\"png\"\r\n        name = \"falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/{}.{}\".format(get_current_time(), houzhui)\r\n        ali_ret = bucket.put_object(name, img)\r\n        link = r\"http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/\" + name\r\n        res = {\r\n            \'code\': 200,\r\n            \'message\': \'上传成功\',\r\n            # 跨域上传只需要返回图像imgUrl即可\r\n            \'data\': link\r\n        }\r\n        return jsonify(res)\r\n```',2,'yuuha999','不浪仙人'),(6,'2024-07-31 14:43:47','Editor.md','Editor.md 文档','slug-Editor.md 文档','# 官方网址帮助\r\n```\r\n快捷键设置 http://editor.md.ipandao.com/examples/custom-keyboard-shortcuts.html\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 文末引入js\r\n```\r\n<script src=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'js/js-guanfang/2.1.1-jquery.min.js\') }}\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/editormd.min.js\') }}\"></script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n# style样式文件\r\n```\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.css\') }}\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.logo.css\') }}\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.logo.min.css\') }}\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.min.css\') }}\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.preview.css\') }}\">\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for(\'static\', filename=\'editor.md-master/css/editormd.preview.min.css\') }}\">\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 自定义style样式文件\r\n```\r\n        h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 .wenzhangneirong{\r\n            font-size: 16px !important;\r\n            font-weight: bold !important;\r\n            margin: 6px !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        h1{\r\n            color: #520202 !important;\r\n            background-color: rgb(225, 240, 235) !important;\r\n            border-radius: 5px !important;\r\n            padding: 6px !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .biaoti{\r\n            font-size: 25px;\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n            background-color: rgb(204, 240, 228);\r\n            border-radius: 5px;\r\n            padding: 6px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .biaotiMain{\r\n            color: rgb(72, 139, 238) !important;\r\n            font-size: 35px !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        /*整体1500*/\r\n        .col-md-9{\r\n            width: 1500px;\r\n            right: 83px;\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\n# js配置\r\n```\r\n        // editormd\r\n        var testEditor;\r\n        $(function () {\r\n            testEditor = editormd(\"test-editormd\", {\r\n                width: \"100%\",\r\n                height: 640,\r\n                syncScrolling: \"single\",\r\n                path: \"{{ url_for(\'static\',filename=\'editor.md-master/lib/\') }}\",\r\n                searchReplace : true,\r\n                flowChart : true,             // 开启流程图支持，默认关闭\r\n                emoji           : true,\r\n                tocm            : true, //对目录解析\r\n\r\n                imageUpload : true,  // 上传图片\r\n                imageFormats : [ \"jpg\", \"jpeg\", \"gif\", \"png\", \"bmp\", \"webp\",\"svg\" ],\r\n                \r\n                // article是蓝图 uploads_pic是访问url\r\n                // imageUploadURL : \"{{ url_for(\'article.uploads_pic_kuayu_self\') }}\",  // 上传图片时指定调用后台的视图函数\r\n                // imageUploadURL : \"{{ url_for(\'article.upload_bendi_shangchuan\') }}\",  // 上传图片时指定调用后台的视图函数\r\n                imageUploadURL : \"{{ url_for(\'article.uploads_pic_paste_self\') }}\",  // 上传图片时指定调用后台的视图函数\r\n\r\n                onload : function() {\r\n                        console.log(\'onload\', this);\r\n                        //加载完成后 配置生成目录\r\n                        testEditor.config(\"tocDropdown\", true); \r\n                        //支持复制，粘贴，拖拽上传文件。\r\n                        initPasteDragImg(this);//必须\r\n                        },\r\n\r\n            });\r\n        });\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 代码块设置滚动条\r\n现在有一个问题就是浏览文章界面，代码过长就会挤到第二行，这样很丑。\r\n\r\n# 设置Ctrl+S保存文章\r\n每次点击保存文章按钮很繁琐，想通过快捷键的方式保存  \r\n可以设置disabledKeyMaps禁用快捷键，禁用某些默认键盘快捷键句柄\r\n```\r\nvar testEditor = editormd(\"test-editormd\", {\r\n    width: \"90%\",\r\n    height: 720,\r\n    path : \'../lib/\',\r\n    disabledKeyMaps : [\r\n        \"Ctrl-B\", \"F11\", \"F10\"  // disable some default keyboard shortcuts handle\r\n    ],\r\n```\r\n通过设置这个\r\n```\r\n    onload : function() {\r\n        var keyMap = {\r\n            \"Ctrl-S\": function(cm) {\r\n                alert(\"Ctrl+S\");\r\n            },\r\n            \"Ctrl-A\": function(cm) { // default Ctrl-A selectAll\r\n                // custom\r\n                alert(\"Ctrl+A\");\r\n                cm.execCommand(\"selectAll\");\r\n            }\r\n        };\r\n\r\n        // setting signle key\r\n        var keyMap2 = {\r\n              \"Ctrl-T\": function(cm) {\r\n                alert(\"Ctrl+T\");\r\n              }\r\n        };\r\n\r\n        this.addKeyMap(keyMap);\r\n        this.addKeyMap(keyMap2);\r\n        this.removeKeyMap(keyMap2);  // remove signle key\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 默认快捷键\r\n```\r\nCtrl+E ::\r\nCtrl+U - \r\nCtrl+I **\r\nCtrl+S 保存\r\nCtrl+D 2024-08-04 10:45:15 星期日\r\nCtrl+F 搜索\r\nCtrl+H ------------\r\nCtrl+K ``\r\nCtrl+L []()\r\nCtrl+B ****\r\n```',2,'yuuha999','不浪仙人'),(7,'2024-08-01 13:03:54','工作记录','新公司工作流程记录','slug-新公司工作流程记录','[TOC]\r\n\r\n# 准备工作\r\n1 安装搜狗/微信/wps/360压缩/百度网盘/谷歌浏览器/360软件管家/sublime_text/python/pycharm  \r\n```\r\nhttps://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-390/\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 配置网络\r\n1 打开F盘 里面会有一个网卡安装  \r\n2 选择 一个网络  \r\n3 网络密码是 3.1415926  \r\n4 开门密码 101030#\r\n\r\n# 安装谷歌\r\n```\r\nhttps://www.google.cn/chrome/\r\n```\r\n\r\n# 安装配置 clash\r\n打开clash --profiles  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz001.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/falsk/py3.10.5_The_Avenue/2024-08-01!13_01_53.png \'\'图片title\'\')  \r\n\r\n```\r\n通过百度网盘分享的文件：1718012682557.yml\r\n链接：https://pan.baidu.com/s/1oN9rKodfsj5QKPB1MFQzcw \r\n提取码：84k7 \r\n--来自百度网盘超级会员V1的分享\r\n```\r\n将这个配置文件拖动到配置里面去  \r\n![图片alt](http://rsgz